Princess Osayomwanbor Peters bụ onye amaara nke ọma site na aha egwu ya Princess Peters bụ onye na-agụ egwú gospel nke Naijiria, onye na-ede egwu, onye n'edekọ ma na-eme ihe nkiri, onye na -eme ihe nkiri na-emepụta ihe nkiri, na onye ọrụ ebere. Ọ malitere ọrụ egwu ya mgbe ọ dị obere ma malite ọrụ egwu na abọm izizi n'afọ 2007 n'okpuru Lighthworld Productions
A mụrụ Peters na Benin City, Edo steeti, Nigeria

Ọ bụ nwa nke asatọ n'ezinụlọ nwere ụmụ iri. Princess nwere NCE ya na Biology na Integrated Science n'afọ 2006 na College of Education Benin, ugbu a Mahadum Tayo Akpata, na Mahadum Benson Idahosa, iji nweta nzere na Mass Communication.
Princess Peters malitere ịbụ abụ n'òtù ukwe ụmụaka nke ụka ya ebe ya na ndị mụrụ ya na-efe ofufe mgbe ahụ
Ọ malitere ọrụ egwu ya na abọm izizi "Kpomwen Ijesu" n'afọ 2007 n'okpuru Lighthworld Productions sochiri ERHUN n'afọ 2011
Kemgbe ahụ, ọ wepụtara egwu egwu na abọm gụnyere, Urhuese, Ose, Ogboviosa na ndị ọzọ.
